Selection_Sort = (array) ->
    for i in [0...array.length]
        min_index = i
        for j in [i + 1...array.length]
            min_index = j if array[j] < array[min_index]

        [array[i], array[min_index]] = [array[min_index], array[i]]
    array

array = [2, 4, 3, 1, 6, 8, 4]
